      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all mechanics and restoration fans! This car is the perfect project for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a vehicle back to life. While it currently requires major mechanical attention and significant repairs to be roadworthy, it offers a fantastic foundation for a dedicated hobbyist or a valuable source of parts. If you're looking for a rewarding challenge at a great price, this is the one for you!",
